    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to be letting this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014I\u2019ve spent more Sunday mornings polishing it than I care to admit! It\u2019s in truly incredible shape, looking just as sharp as the day it first hit the road. It drives like an absolute dream and has been pampered every single mile. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been genuinely loved and kept in top-tier condition, you\u2019ve found it. Come on over, let\u2019s have a chat, and see if this is the perfect new addition to your garage!",
