    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an absolute collector-spec E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 naturally aspirated V8. This unit is surgically clean, with critical preventative maintenance already addressed: rod bearings replaced with VAC coated shells and ARP hardware to eliminate the platform's primary failure point. The 7-speed M-DCT has been optimized with a GTS transmission flash for crisp, lightning-fast engagement and increased clamping pressure. Zero subframe deflection and no weeping from the throttle actuators or VANOS solenoids. The Electronic Damper Control (EDC) provides a stiff, communicative chassis response, and the engine pulls linearly all the way to its 8,400 RPM redline. This is a high-compression masterpiece for the discerning driver who understands mechanical provenance. No codes, no leaks, just pure atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
